item.title: How do i get on to a server using( ham)
item.dc:creator: @udluv2 udluv2
item.description:
@udluv2 wrote:

download ham and the click the triangle thing down the bottom and type in the server name and password and click join. Then open up ur moparscape and go to file>new server and enter the i.p address they give u. Click enter and enter ur username and pass. Click enter. Enjoy. Hope this helps
